who they are.

801
00:54:02,030 --> 00:54:03,316
Harry Dighby.

802
00:54:04,408 --> 00:54:06,149
And Walter Hill.

803
00:54:08,328 --> 00:54:09,318
Red.

804
00:54:15,085 --> 00:54:16,701
