didn't you, Harry?

812
00:54:55,834 --> 00:54:57,200
No, no, no, no.

813
00:54:57,294 --> 00:54:59,752
Look me in the eye and tell me
you don't have the plans.

814
00:54:59,838 --> 00:55:01,830
Right in the eye.

815
00:55:01,924 --> 00:55:04,632
