933
01:01:35,609 --> 01:01:37,817
Harry, would you
give him the plans?

934
01:01:38,904 --> 01:01:41,146
How's it coming along,
Mr. Dighby?

935
01:01:41,990 --> 01:01:43,151
Harry?

