949
01:03:21,506 --> 01:03:23,919
Well,
the plans are yours.

950
01:03:27,053 --> 01:03:28,919
- Can you, uh— Mr. Finley?
- Mr. Finley.

951
01:03:29,848 --> 01:03:32,056
Hurry. Hurry.

952
01:03:37,772 --> 01:03:41,311
Walter! Oh, no!
