955
01:03:49,242 --> 01:03:50,608
You!

956
01:03:51,453 --> 01:03:52,534
You!

957
01:03:55,874 --> 01:04:00,494
No! Stop it!
Stop it! Please!

958
01:04:00,587 --> 01:04:02,795
Stop it!
This is enough!

959
01:04:02,881 --> 01:04:05,589
