974
01:04:46,174 --> 01:04:49,838
Ohh, when I—
Oh, and, and...

975
01:04:49,928 --> 01:04:52,170
And make no mistake
about it, Mr. Worth.

976
01:04:52,263 --> 01:04:53,595
Make no mistake about it.

977
01:04:53,681 --> 01:04:56,344
Oh, yes, indeed,
you fancy yourself an intellectual,

